snippet.title: Battery Jam - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Available on Steam Early Access now!

Use the Boombox to smash your opponents, capture their tiles and dominate the arena! Take on your friends in Battery Jam, a local multiplayer game of competitive territorial mayhem!

Coming to Steam Early Access in January!


Website - https://www.batteryjam.com/
Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/751330
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/batteryjam/
Twitter - https://www.twitter.com/BatteryJamGame
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/batteryjamgame/
Reddit - https://www.reddit.com/r/batteryjam/
